<div class="title">Greatest Drug Known to Man</div>
<div class="substance">Diazepam (Valium)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Mad+Merv&Exact=1">Mad Merv</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Mad Merv. "Greatest Drug Known to Man: An Experience with Diazepam (Valium) (exp68568)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 22, 2008. erowid.org/exp/68568</div>

<br/>



